18 May 2015As part of the Pre-Budget Vote for the Department of Communications, the Deputy Minister of Communications Stella Ndabeni-Abrahams will on Tuesday 19 May 2015, engage with journalism students of the Cape Peninsula University of Technology (CPUT).Details are as follows: Date: Tuesday, 19 May 2015 Time: 10:00am Venue: Roeland Street Campus, Photography Room (2.14) on the second floor.RSVP and Enquiries: Ms Senzeni Ngubane Tel: 012 473 0402 / 060 616 9668; Email: senzeni@doc.gov.zaJoin the engagement using the hashtag #BudgetVote2015Issued by Government Communications (GCIS) on behalf of The Ministry of Communications